##Editing MIDI
Versions of Harrison Mixbus through version 2.4 do not support MIDI editing. Mixbus does support MIDI communication and control. But Mixbus has no provisions for software instruments or MIDI tracks. Harrison suggests that these features and capabilities may be in future releases.  
*Velocity
*Quantization
*Control Change data
*MIDI monitor(through)
*Other MIDI editing tips
*Adding software instruments
*Other MIDI tips

